But my husband ordered a simple alfredo dish.
He says the true test of good italian is to order something simple, and if they do that right, they likely do the rest very well.
That alfredo sauce was the BEST alfredo sauce I've ever tasted.
YUM.
It's close by to our house, so we'll definitely be going back!

