He keeps a tight ship and whatever he's doing, I suggest he keeps it going.
Try anything with piccata sauce.
I myself, take pride in my piccata sauce (having learned the recipe from grandpa who resides in Florence, Italy) I would have to say this is much better.
So authentic you won't find better anywhere in the area.
